                We research visual recognition, image understanding, object detection, and scene
                analysis, with applications in autonomous systems and visual AI.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Biometrics column */}
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="28"
                height="28"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <path d="M2 12C2 6.5 6.5 2 12 2a10 10 0 0 1 8 4" />
                <path d="M5 19.5C5.5 18 6 15 6 12c0-.7.12-1.37.34-2" />
                <path d="M17.29 21.02c.12-.6.43-2.3.5-3.02" />
                <path d="M12 10a2 2 0 0 0-2 2c0 1.02-.1 2.51-.26 4" />
                <path d="M8.65 22c.21-.66.45-1.32.57-2" />
                <path d="M14 13.12c0 2.38 0 6.38-1 8.88" />
                <path d="M2 16h.01" />
                <path d="M21.8 16c.2-2 .131-5.354 0-6" />
                <path d="M9 6.8a6 6 0 0 1 9 5.2c0 .47 0 1.17-.02 2" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
                Biometrics
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
                We develop methods for face recognition, person re-identification, and
                biometric authentication using deep learning techniques.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* 3D Computer Vision column */}
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="28"
                height="28"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <path d="M12 3l9 5v8l-9 5-9-5V8l9-5z" />
                <path d="M12 3v10" />
                <path d="M3 8l9 5" />
                <path d="M21 8l-9 5" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
                3D Computer Vision
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
                We work on 3D reconstruction, depth estimation, and geometric understanding
                of visual data to bridge the gap between 2D imagery and 3D scenes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 text-center mt-10 leading-relaxed">
          Our research combines deep learning with geometric and perceptual principles to build
          robust, real-world visual intelligence systems.
        </p>

        <!-- Highlights -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-12 mb-8 text-center">Highlights</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          {highlights.map(item => (
            <a
              href={item.data.link}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow"
            >
              <div class="bg-gray-100 h-40 flex items-center justify-center p-4">
                <img
                  src={getImagePath(item.data.image)}
                  alt={item.data.title}
                  class="max-h-full max-w-full object-contain"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-1">{item.data.title}</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">{item.data.description}</p>
              </div>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


